'''Masepala ya Walter Sisulu''' (''Walter Sisulu Local Municipality'') ke masepala go feta [[Karolwana sa Joe Gqabi]] wa porofense [[Kapa Botlhaba]] ka moka [[Aferika Borwa]]. The municipality was formed by the merging of Maletswai and Gariep Local Municipality immediately after the August 2016 Local Municipal Elections.

Motse-kgolo ya Walter Sisulu ke [[Aliwal North]].

